e in creativity hard work and corporate partnership’s power to build our company’s future from the shareholders to the programmer everyone plays a key role in raising our corporate value and from that we will be able to develop technological projects that will transform the world we live in current and future focus web applications future technology everything is possible latest news  jul  in news wagergang project is on is way northlionholding corp is proud to announce that the wagergang project is on its way  aug  in news we are pleased to announce that our filing to become a public company has been deposited at sec for review we are pleased to announce that our filing to become a public company has been contact us we care about your passion and your ideas contact us north lion holding corp private company information  bloomberg july    am et professional services company overview of north lion holding corp snapshot people company overview north lion holding corp a management holding company provides assistance to businesses in various industries the company also offers consulting services for startup growing plans management and marketing in addition it provides services in the areas of branding experience factory and contract it projects business consultation fast growing business and supporting and financing the company was incorporated in  and is based in lewes delaware  coastal highwaylewes de united statesfounded in  phone  wwwnorthlionholdingcom key executives for north lion holding corp vincent deblois chief executive officer marc fortier chief financial officer vanessa martel chief operating officer compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region  payroll  hr services inc united states  water audit llc united states collegecom inc united states d research llc united states  partners llc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile